Package app

Class Person

java.lang.Object
app.Person
All Implemented Interfaces:
PersonInterface, Comparable<Person>
public class Person extends Object implements PersonInterface, Comparable<Person>
Represents a person with first name, last name, and age. Implements PersonInterface for walking, running functionality, and Comparable for age-based comparisons.
